          q: 'Do you offer custom solutions?',
          a: 'Yes, we specialize in tailored solutions. Contact us to discuss your specific requirements.',
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      category: 'Pricing',
      items: [
        {
          q: 'How is pricing structured?',
          a: 'Pricing varies by service and scope. We provide transparent quotes after understanding your needs.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Do you offer discounts?',
          a: 'We offer flexible pricing options and special rates for long-term partnerships and group engagements.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Is there a free consultation?',
          a: 'Yes, we offer an initial consultation to understand your needs and recommend appropriate services.',
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      category: 'Academy',
      items: [
        {
          q: 'How long are the modules?',
          a: 'Module duration varies from 4 to 12 weeks depending on complexity and depth. Check individual modules for specifics.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Is there a certificate after completion?',
          a: 'Yes, you\'ll receive a certificate of completion after successfully finishing a module.',
        },
        {
          q: 'Can I work at my own pace?',
          a: 'Yes, our academy modules are designed to be flexible, allowing you to progress at your own pace.',
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      category: 'Support',
      items: [
        {
          q: 'How do I get support?',
          a: 'Contact us via email at nioeze@yahoomail.com or through WhatsApp for immediate assistance.',
        },
        {
          q: 'What if I have a technical issue?',
          a: 'Our technical support team is available to help. Describe your issue and we\'ll guide you through resolution.',
        },
